---
import SectionLabel from "../ui/SectionLabel.astro";

interface Props {
  id?: string;
}

const { id } = Astro.props;

const items = [
  {
    number: "01",
    textEn:
      "No two systems start from the same place — the engagement begins from where yours is.",
    textEs:
      "No hay dos sistemas que partan del mismo punto — el proyecto empieza donde está el tuyo.",
    delay: 60,
  },
  {
    number: "02",
    textEn:
      "So it starts with questions, not a pitch. What's the architecture actually doing? What does the team already know? Where can we move fast, and where should we slow down?",
    textEs:
      "¿Qué está haciendo realmente la arquitectura? ¿Qué sabe ya el equipo? ¿Dónde conviene avanzar rápido y dónde frenar? Se empieza preguntando, no vendiendo.",
    delay: 120,
  },
  {
    number: "03",
    textEn:
      "The scope, the pace, the format — all of that adapts. The judgement behind it doesn't.",
    textEs:
      "El alcance, el ritmo, la forma: todo eso se adapta. El criterio detrás, no.",
    delay: 180,
  },
  {
    number: "04",
    textEn:
      "That might start with an architecture review, a focused technical assessment, support for something already underway, or a longer engagement — sized to what is actually needed.",
    textEs:
      "Puede empezar con una revisión de arquitectura, una evaluación técnica puntual, apoyo a algo que ya está en marcha, o un proyecto más largo — según lo que realmente haga falta.",
    delay: 220,
  },
];
---

<section id={id} aria-labelledby="collab-heading" class="collab-section">
  <div class="collab-section__inner">
    <SectionLabel label="04 — Collaboration" counter="04 / 05" />

    <h2
      data-reveal
      data-d="60"
      id="collab-heading"
      class="collab-section__headline"
    >
      <span lang="en"
        >Every engagement begins with the system you already have.</span
      >
      <span lang="es">Todo proyecto empieza con el sistema que ya tienes.</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="collab-section__split">
      <div class="collab-section__items">
        {
          items.map((item) => (
            <div data-reveal data-d={item.delay} class="collab-item">
              <span class="collab-item__number">{item.number}</span>
              <p class="collab-item__text">
                <span lang="en">{item.textEn}</span>
                <span lang="es">{item.textEs}</span>
              </p>
            </div>
          ))
        }
      </div>

      <!-- Adapts / constant diagram -->
      <div
        data-reveal
        data-d="140"
        class="collab-diagram"
        role="img"
        data-label-en="Diagram: scope, pace and form of engagement vary per client, but the engineering judgement applied to them stays constant"
        data-label-es="Diagrama: el alcance, el ritmo y la forma del proyecto varían según el cliente, pero el criterio de ingeniería aplicado se mantiene constante"
      >
        <span class="collab-diagram__label">
          <span lang="en">What adapts, what doesn't</span>
          <span lang="es">Qué se adapta, qué no</span>
        </span>

        <div class="collab-diagram__inputs">
          <div class="collab-diagram__input">
            <span class="collab-diagram__input-tag">
              <span lang="en">Varies</span><span lang="es">Varía</span>
            </span>
            <span class="collab-diagram__input-value">
              <span lang="en">Scope</span><span lang="es">Alcance</span>
            </span>
          </div>
          <div class="collab-diagram__input">
            <span class="collab-diagram__input-tag">
              <span lang="en">Varies</span><span lang="es">Varía</span>
            </span>
            <span class="collab-diagram__input-value">
              <span lang="en">Pace</span><span lang="es">Ritmo</span>
            </span>
          </div>
          <div class="collab-diagram__input">
            <span class="collab-diagram__input-tag">
              <span lang="en">Varies</span><span lang="es">Varía</span>
            </span>
            <span class="collab-diagram__input-value">
              <span lang="en">Form of engagement</span>
              <span lang="es">Forma del proyecto</span>
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div aria-hidden="true" class="collab-diagram__paths">
          <svg
            viewBox="0 0 300 60"
            preserveAspectRatio="none"
            class="collab-diagram__paths-svg"
          >
            <path
              d="M 50 0 C 50 30, 150 20, 150 55"
              fill="none"
              stroke="var(--line2)"
              stroke-width="1.5"></path>
            <path
              d="M 150 0 L 150 55"
              fill="none"
              stroke="var(--line2)"
              stroke-width="1.5"></path>
            <path
              d="M 250 0 C 250 30, 150 20, 150 55"
              fill="none"
              stroke="var(--line2)"
              stroke-width="1.5"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>

        <div class="collab-diagram__output">
          <span class="collab-diagram__output-tag">
            <span lang="en">Stays constant, every time</span>
            <span lang="es">Se mantiene constante, siempre</span>
          </span>
          <span class="collab-diagram__output-value">
            <span lang="en">Engineering judgement</span>
            <span lang="es">Criterio de ingeniería</span>
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p data-reveal data-d="80" class="collab-section__closing">
      <span lang="en"
        >Success isn't the delivery date. It's a team that understands the
        system, owns what was built, and can make the next change alone.</span
      >
      <span lang="es"
        >El éxito no se mide por la fecha de entrega. El mejor resultado es un
        equipo que entiende el sistema, se apropia de lo construido y puede
        seguir cambiándolo solo.</span
      >
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .collab-section {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    padding: clamp(6rem, 12vh, 9.375rem) clamp(1.25rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
    background: var(--bg2);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .collab-section__inner {
    max-width: 1160px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .collab-section__headline {
    margin: 0 0 56px;
    max-width: 700px;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4.2vw, 3rem);
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .collab-section__split {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.15fr 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  @media (max-width: 980px) {
    .collab-section__split {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .collab-item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 32px 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
    padding: 20px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .collab-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .collab-item__number {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .collab-item__text {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  /* Diagram */
  .collab-diagram {
    padding: 26px;
    border-radius: 18px;
    background: var(--bg2);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .collab-diagram__label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 9.5px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink3);
  }

  .collab-diagram__inputs {
    margin-top: 18px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .collab-diagram__input {
    padding: 12px 8px;
    border-radius: 11px;
    background: var(--bg3);
    border: 1px dashed var(--line2);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .collab-diagram__input-tag {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 9px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink3);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .collab-diagram__input-value {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.25;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .collab-diagram__paths {
    position: relative;
    height: 44px;
    margin: 2px 6px 0;
  }

  .collab-diagram__paths-svg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    overflow: visible;
  }

  .collab-diagram__output {
    padding: 20px 22px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
    text-align: center;
  }

  .collab-diagram__output-tag {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 9.5px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .collab-diagram__output-value {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 19px;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: #fff;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
  }

  /* Closing */
  .collab-section__closing {
    margin: 56px 0 0;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: clamp(1.1875rem, 2.1vw, 1.5rem);
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    padding-top: 28px;
    border-top: 2px solid var(--ink);
  }
</style>
